>>quote<<
!!!Designing for Colour-Blind Users
Author: Christine Rigden

Colour-blind computer users see things differently from most people,
but this is seldom considered in the design of software or web
pages. This article offers a simple technique for simulating the
differences, to help designers and developers avoid disadvantaging
their users.
